<span id="freeTextContainer9977818528403081177">3.5/5<br/>Historian poet. Poet of desire. Poet of antiquity. <br/><br/>Overall, this is a very well done collection of Cavafy&apos;s poetry. I enjoyed the robust introduction and notes. I would definitely recommend it for people interested in Cavafy&apos;s work. As for the poems themselves, many I adored, some I liked, and some I didn&apos;t care for at all.</span>
  <span id="freeText9977818528403081177" style="display:none">3.5/5<br />Historian poet. Poet of desire. Poet of antiquity. <br /><br />Overall, this is a very well done collection of Cavafy's poetry. I enjoyed the robust introduction and notes. I would definitely recommend it for people interested in Cavafy's work. As for the poems themselves, many I adored, some I liked, and some I didn't care for at all.</span>
