<span id="freeTextContainer1954179153629007098">I read this piecemeal, skipping around. I know some of the historical and classical references but not all; I&apos;m glad there are such extensive notes. Some poems were gorgeous but others made no sense. I liked best and will always remember &quot;Candles&quot; and &quot;Ithaka.&quot;</span>
  <span id="freeText1954179153629007098" style="display:none">I read this piecemeal, skipping around. I know some of the historical and classical references but not all; I'm glad there are such extensive notes. Some poems were gorgeous but others made no sense. I liked best and will always remember "Candles" and "Ithaka."</span>
